title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 29 2022
description:
Andy McCarthy of National Review joins Buck to do a deep dive on the Biden investigation, gives us his theory on how the Bidens could skate on a small tax evasion charge. Journos lament: Biden WH too professional to report on. May 6th: Clay's mom and Buck's mom on the air. Friday VIP mailbag. Psaki stands up for Soviet Mary Poppins.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
